To read in Donor SRAs:

1. Start by copying link into VS-Code and get your new Pipeline_Project_Samples folder

For each of the four sample files: 
2. Go to the NCBI website, filter for SRA and search the run number associated with the SRA 
3. Once in the SRA, scroll down to runs and click the run number - this will send you to a new page 
4. At this new page press data access, and scroll down to SRA archival data
5. Copy paste the link for SRA Normalized. 
6. in your terminal diectory type wget <link> 
    this will download a zip file for each read 
7. Use fasterq-dump./ SRA_number to unzip files
8. you will get two fastq files for each SRA number: a forward and reverse 
9. Repeat for each SRA run number
